sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Driver
    participant DriverApp as Driver App
    participant IncidentController as Incident Controller
    participant IncidentModel as Incident DB
    participant NotificationService as Notification Service
    participant CoordinatorApp as Coordinator App
    participant Coordinator

    Driver->>DriverApp: Navigate to Report Incident
    DriverApp-->>Driver: Display incident form
    
    Driver->>DriverApp: Submit type description severity
    DriverApp->>DriverApp: Capture GPS location
    
    DriverApp->>IncidentController: POST /api/incidents
    
    IncidentController->>IncidentController: Validate payload
    IncidentController->>IncidentModel: insertOne status open
    IncidentModel-->>IncidentController: Created incident
    
    IncidentController->>NotificationService: notifyCoordinators
    NotificationService->>CoordinatorApp: FCM push notification
    
    IncidentController-->>DriverApp: 201 Incident reported
    DriverApp-->>Driver: Incident reported successfully
    
    CoordinatorApp-->>Coordinator: Display notification
    Coordinator->>CoordinatorApp: Tap notification
    CoordinatorApp-->>Coordinator: View incident details
